headline: Despite Campus Closure, Kellogg’s San Francisco Immersion Will Continue: Dean
summary: Northwestern will close its San Francisco campus based on the 18th floor in the Financial District at 44 Montgomery Street, the former headquarters of Wells Fargo bank.
